State Of Alabama EMS Protocols - 9th edition effective January 2018.

Full State Of Alabama Patient Care Protocols, EMT - Paramedic. Fully indexed. Subsequent updates will push to the device on the date they become effective.

Requires any free PDF reader, but it is not simply a PDF file. All data resident in the app.

Money back within 90 days if not satisfied, just email support at info@apps4ems.com.
